---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Capabilities | Foremost Machine, Inc.">
  <section class="section-shell">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">Capabilities</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-slate-300">Our team supports commercial buyers that need repeatable quality, responsive communication, and scalable part production.</p>
    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">Precision CNC Milling & Turning</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">3-axis and multi-axis workflows for complex geometry, repeatability, and tolerance-critical components.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">Material Range</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Aluminum, carbon and stainless steels, brass, engineering plastics, and customer-specified stock.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">Quality & Traceability</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Inspection reports, first-article support, and material cert handling to fit purchasing and QA workflows.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><h2 class="text-xl text-white">Production Support</h2><p class="mt-2 text-slate-300">Forecast collaboration, blanket orders, and practical lead-time planning for recurring demand.</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
      <a href="/request-access" class="rounded-md bg-brand-500 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-white hover:bg-brand-700">Request Access</a>
      <a href="/industries" class="rounded-md border border-slate-600 px-5 py-3 font-semibold text-slate-100 hover:border-slate-400">View Industries</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
